            en: "The key issue in deed-fee calculation is not only the rate but whether the declared sale price reflects the actual transaction. Revolving fund charges should not be treated as a single universal fixed amount either; since they may vary by transaction type and official tariff, handling them as an optional scenario produces a more reliable total cost view.",
